purpose: (Clinical Focus: Capture anticholinergic medications),(Data Element Scope: Anticholinergic medications defined using American Geriatrics Society 2015 Beers Criteria Update Expert Panel. J Am Geriatr Soc. 2015;63:2227-2246.),(Inclusion Criteria: Beers Criteria anticholinergic medications linking use to potential cognitive impairment),(Exclusion Criteria: Other anticholinergic medications)
